des:
A skill focuses on what are the expectations of youths or youngster of India regarding any field. It shows what are the major changes that today's generation wants from its country for its prosperity and wellness.
This skill shares a general perspective of the citizen belonging to India who wants to create strong foundation in every aspect whether its an education, governmental laws etc.
